ABOUT METAVERSEZILLA


WHAT IS METAVERSEZILLA


MetaverseZila is a DeFi Token issued on Binance Smart Chain (BEP-20) designed to serve the Metaverse NFT and Gaming Industry, with three simple features implemented at its core; Static Reward + LP Acquisition + Marketing


HOW IT WORKS

Each transaction (buy, sell or transfer) attracts a 8% fee, which is split in three ways:
- 1% Redistributed to all existing holders.
- 5% Marketing/Development.
- 2% Added as Liquidity (LP).









https://github.com/metaversezilla/smartcontract/blob/main/smartcontract.sol







